Love you.

642
00:27:17,364 --> 00:27:19,098
Huh. huh.

643
00:27:19,170 --> 00:27:21,305
I think i have
something for you.

644
00:27:21,379 --> 00:27:22,713
Actually, i'm here
to talk about liam.

645
00:27:22,784 --> 00:27:24,017
Oh, stop right there.

646
00:27:24,090 --> 00:27:25,791
What the hell
is wrong with you people?

647
00:27:25,899 --> 00:27:27,633
I already told the press

648
00:27:27,739 --> 00:27:31,308
That i don't give interviews
about my former clients.

649
00:27:31,386 --> 00:27:33,554
I'm dr. jack gallagher.
i'm his psychiatrist.

650
00:27:36,073 --> 00:27:38,608
He's in trouble, maggie.

651
00:27:38,683 --> 00:27:40,150
I need information,

652
00:27:40,225 --> 00:27:41,825
Anything you can tell me
about his past.

653
00:27:43,269 --> 00:27:45,704
[ sighs ] i had a feeling
that someone like you

