Would show up
at my door one day.

655
00:27:49,359 --> 00:27:50,192
Have a seat.

656
00:27:52,407 --> 00:27:54,208
[ crickets chirping ]

657
00:27:58,565 --> 00:27:59,865
[ chuckles ]

658
00:27:59,971 --> 00:28:02,506
I just had a really
interesting phone call.

659
00:28:02,616 --> 00:28:04,183
Nice for you.

660
00:28:04,287 --> 00:28:06,055
<i>yeah, it was
from a daily news reporter.</i>

661
00:28:06,162 --> 00:28:08,663
She was looking for confirmation
for an anonymous tip

662
00:28:08,773 --> 00:28:10,640
