from in the hospital.

663
00:28:10,714 --> 00:28:12,181
I've said it before --

664
00:28:12,256 --> 00:28:14,257
Security here
is practically nonexistent.

665
00:28:14,362 --> 00:28:15,662
The place is a sieve.
yeah.

666
00:28:15,736 --> 00:28:16,636
What sort of tip?

667
00:28:16,738 --> 00:28:18,071
Well, that liam mcbride

668
00:28:18,145 --> 00:28:20,180
Wasn't staying on
to continue his research.

669
00:28:20,287 --> 00:28:21,954
In fact, he'd had
a huge breakdown

670
00:28:22,029 --> 00:28:23,830
As a result
of his treatment here.

671
00:28:23,935 --> 00:28:25,535
Whoops.
yeah.

672
00:28:25,609 --> 00:28:26,542
What was
your response?

673
00:28:26,611 --> 00:28:27,845
No comment.

674
00:28:27,919 --> 00:28:29,653
They're going
with the story?

675
00:28:29,760 --> 00:28:31,194
Not without
confirmation.

676
00:28:31,265 --> 00:28:33,032
What surprises me,
particularly seeing

677
00:28:33,138 --> 00:28:35,373
As that you were way out
in front of the press

678
00:28:35,482 --> 00:28:36,649
On this matter,

679
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:39,054
Is that
they didn't call you.

680
00:28:39,129 --> 00:28:40,796
<i>that is surprising.</i>

681
00:28:40,871 --> 00:28:44,440
Perhaps they have yet
to get to me.

682
00:28:44,521 --> 00:28:46,389
Of course, my response
would be the same as yours.

683
00:28:46,458 --> 00:28:49,294
Do you really think this is the
way you'll get rid of jack --

684
00:28:49,407 --> 00:28:51,942
