Ohh!

707
00:30:08,428 --> 00:30:09,796
Oh!

708
00:30:09,869 --> 00:30:10,803
[ grunting ]

709
00:30:14,756 --> 00:30:15,856
N-no!

710
00:30:29,081 --> 00:30:31,215
[ ding! ]

711
00:30:32,127 --> 00:30:34,295
[ birds chirping ]

712
00:30:34,403 --> 00:30:37,639
